*****
[2] 9-year-old in Fujian
Date: Sun 5 May 2013
Source: The Standard, Breaking New [edited]
http://www.thestandard.com.hk/breaking_news_detail.asp?id=35746&icid=a&d_str=

(H7N9 watch) Infection count in Fujian up to five
-----------------------------------------
One more case of human infection of the H7N9 flu virus strain have been confirmed in Fujian, bringing the total to five in the province. A 9-year-old boy had fever on April 26 and was admitted to the hospital on April 27. He has fully recovered. In mainland, a total of 128 people have been infected with the H7N9 flu virus, corresponding to 26 deaths.

