[There are some discrepancies in the numbers of confirmed cases and deaths, depending on the date and time of of recording of cases and the reporting of deaths. It would seem that the numbers of cases are declining, but in the absence of population numbers and information on diagnostic capabilities in the different provinces, this is difficult to assess.

A map of the provinces of China can be accessed at: http://www.sacu.org/provmap.html. - Mod.CP]
